od checks if namespace exists using read_namespace\n- [ ] Verify method creates namespace if it doesn't exist (404 status)\n- [ ] Verify method logs when namespace is created\n- [ ] Verify method handles ApiException for 404 correctly\n- [ ] Verify method re-raises non-404 exceptions\n- [ ] Verify method uses correct namespace from instance variable\n\n**Verification**: Run unit test for _ensure_namespace with mocked CoreV1Api\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: Verify KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent method signature\n- [ ] Verify deploy_agent method exists with correct signature\n- [ ] Verify agent_name parameter is str\n- [ ] Verify image_url parameter is str\n- [ ] Verify port parameter is int\n- [ ] Verify entrypoint parameter is Optional[str]\n- [ ] Verify replicas parameter is int with default 1\n- [ ] Verify node_port parameter is Optional[int]\n- [ ] Verify env_vars parameter is Optional[Dict[str, str]]\n- [ ] Verify return type is Dict[str, Any]\n\n**Verification**: Review k8s_provider.py and verify method signature matches design\n\n","exit":0,"description":"Verify tasks.md file content","truncated":false},"title":"Verify tasks.md file content","time":{"start":1775875759631,"end":1775875759649}}}}
